source.name: IDES -  Claimants for regular (non-Federal) unemployment insurance benefits dashboard, Statewide
source.description: The Dashboard contains information on Illinois claimants for regular (non-Federal) unemployment insurance benefits. The reports feature claimant information by education, age, and military status. Explanations of definitions and methodology are included in the technical notes.
